sub_title: MSc, Finance Data and Automation Specialist
summary: I am 23 years old and I have a rather international background. I have studied in Slovenia, England and Netherlands. I am currently working in Amsterdam fulltime at Creative Clicks as a Finance Data and Automation Specialist as part of the Data Quality and Finance Innovation team. My everyday duties include anything from creating dynamic reports and building financial dashboards to modelling RPA processes. My highest degree of education is my MSc in Finance and Technology, which fits perfectly with my professional interest in Data Analytics and IT in combination with Finance and Accounting.
